creator: Fulfillment.Global
descriptionHtml:
This application is made for people specifically working in our warehouse. Public Users can also use this application to scan barcode of the product and its availability in our warehouse.
Key features of this application include following:
Barcode scanner to scan items in the warehouse.
Update Status of items i.e. Available, Missing, InTransit, Borrowed etc.
Add comments against items.
Items belong to SKU and Locations and this application is used to segregate items according to its location and statuses.
Verification process in different types such as lump sump, item by item etc.
descriptionShort: Fulfillment is to manage inventory in the warehouse by employees.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Put a barcode on Warranty screen.
- Swap Save and Cancel button
- Bug! Here, if you tap anywhere, the waiting window will disappear.
- Once a photo taken, taking a while to show in the list.
- When expand to show all photos, add a header
